title: My Honor
body:
Its been 250+ games of positivity, 2 MONTHS, and much question. When will I get honor level 1? Ive been getting decent honors (lately from premades just cause we play with eachother). So..... where is my honor level 1?
Thanks!
Rynojos

replies.body: Keep it up!  We don't have a visible meter to offer, but based on the severity of the account it could be a bit.  Keep playing honorable, and you'll make it through!
